parameters: Mine Worker Guard: Sigh... I can't focus on my work.
Mine Worker Guard: Who are you guys?

Sophia the priestess: We have come as messengers of the
Imiserinos shrine maiden.

Mine Worker Guard: Our prayers have been answered!
Messengers of the shrine maiden, I want you to listen to
what I have to say.

Priestess Sophia: I see... So you don't have the courage to
confess.

Mine Worker Guard: After being together for so long, what
words should I use to convey my feelings?

Priestess Sophia: Isn't it unnecessary to force yourself to
choose your words carefully? Isn't it more important to
convey your feelings in your own words?

Priestess Sophia: Have confidence in your feelings, as they
reach the Imiserinos shrine maiden.
Mine Worker Guard: Thank you! Please witness my confession!

Laundry Woman Land: What's going on? Why did you call us
here all of a sudden... Who are these people?
Mine Worker Guard: I love you, will you marry me!

Laundry Woman Land: Huh...!? What are you suddenly saying?
Are you joking?

Mine Worker Guard: My love has moved Imiserinos! Please
marry me and I will make you happy, I beg you!

Laundry Woman Land: Well, fine. We've been stuck together
for a while, after all...

Mine Worker Guard: Oh! Land, thank you! Our twisted fate is
eternal!

Mine Worker Guard: Representatives of the shrine maidens,
please convey my gratitude to the Imiserinos shrine maiden
as well!

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, I can't help but feel jealous when I
see something like this.

Laundry Woman Land: You're so noisy... Well, I guess I'm
grateful.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Mine Worker Guard: I'm glad you mustered up the courage! May
the blessings of Imiserinos be with you too!

Laundry Girl Land: 'You're a man who can't function without
me, since a long time ago.'

Laundry Girl Land: I appreciate it, please take this with
you.

events.name: QI｢イミセリノスの巫女からの依頼｣
